text: Toby Myles (born July 23, 1975) is a former American football tackle. He played for the New York Giants in 1999 and for the Cleveland Browns and Oakland Raiders in 2001. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:American football tackles Category:Mississippi State Bulldogs football players Category:Jackson State Tigers football players Category:New York Giants players Category:Cleveland Browns players Category:Oakland Raiders players
